Like🙏Subscribe🙏Follow🙏Retweet</span></strong><br />\nFacebook:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standwithhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandwithhk&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=3a3d741e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standwithhk</a><br />\nTwitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=b573459f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK</a><br />\nInstagram:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/standwithhk_\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fstandwithhk_&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=20f5cce6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/standwithhk_</a><br />\nYouTube:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyi42Y5o1ksO_yFItyHW7Jw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCyi42Y5o1ksO_yFItyHW7Jw&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=43f04f19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyi42Y5o1ksO_yFItyHW7Jw</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">傳說7.21恐怖份子黑社會圖上武器之一<br />\n7.27香港人不站出來追究<br />\n這種恐怖襲擊將會在18區無處不在</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">中聯辦背後策劃證據</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/videos/vb.454004001340790/694413694332018/?type=2&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcantonese.rfa%2Fvideos%2Fvb.454004001340790%2F694413694332018%2F%3Ftype%3D2%26theater&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=69862052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/videos/vb.454004001340790/694413694332018/?type=2&amp;theater</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sUx81OM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsUx81OM.png&h=2ee50185&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n🎆光復香港🎆時代革命🎆爭取五大訴求🎆<br />\n📢1. 全面撤回送中條例<br />\n📢2. 撤銷6.12暴動定性&nbsp;<br />\n📢3. 釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究&nbsp;<br />\n📢4. 全面實行雙普選&nbsp;<br />\n📢5. 成立獨立調查委員會，追究黑警濫用暴力，徹查警黑勾結7.21元朗恐襲<br />\n<strong>7.28 14:00 最後底線，否則行動升級</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">睇到最底 內容包括：「運動時間」 「聯署」 《會加入新聯署 記得去簽》 白宮需要係電郵內確認先叫完成 記得係電郵㩒連結 唔好懶 所有活動必須同時進行</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">持續不合作運動「兄弟爬山，各自努力」<br />\n🥳 - 18區連儂場<br />\n🥳 - 沙田新城市廣場</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n🥳7.27 元朗反恐襲 - 踢走鄉黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1355504\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1355504</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hj9SJ1x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHj9SJ1x.jpg&h=b4499f0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n🥳7.28 母忘上環 - 追究上環開槍責任<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356713</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xONthmo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxONthmo.jpg&h=e70b88ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n🥳8.4 將軍澳反送中大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356143&nbsp;\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356143&nbsp;</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n🥳8.4 港島西大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356505</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HLCEo1g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHLCEo1g.png&h=5e9e8f32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請各位努力推po以提出遊行時間修訂<br />\n已取消或延期:<br />\n<br />\n兩條戰線同樣重要 但係請各位心水清&nbsp;<br />\n任何一方都不能忽視 以防誤中港共圈套<br />\n亦避免被各方妖孽分散注意力 必須將火力對準政權<br />\n政府務必回應五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">簽咗都要🙏廣傳🙏快夠數💪唔好話冇用就唔做，唔理效果有咩都必撐，團結是力量</span></strong>💪<br />\n<br />\n<strong>YAHOO 公投7.21元朗襲擊事件</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/poll/b8409c30-af4f-11e9-bc33-816028901f44\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fpoll%2Fb8409c30-af4f-11e9-bc33-816028901f44&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=bcc4004c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/poll/b8409c30-af4f-11e9-bc33-816028901f44</a><br />\n🖕🖕🖕見指中聯辦😡😡勾結香港黑社會😡😡<strong>策劃元朗恐怖襲擊聯署</strong>🖕🖕🖕<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 23, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/restore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frestore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again-0&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=708a56ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/restore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again-0</a><br />\n🧐🧐<strong>元朗黑夜連登獨立調查委員會</strong>🧐🧐<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 23, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/34AmN69rRScNafEC9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F34AmN69rRScNafEC9&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=b580a326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/34AmN69rRScNafEC9</a><br />\n🤬🤬<strong>要求馬會撤銷何君堯會藉</strong>🤬🤬<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 23, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSchg3S-rvjk7DOky6yBCoby8EQMytbBE1eyYGyQe5rkIpSFcg/viewform?fbclid=IwAR0miS_G0dUlNRbwJeACAkr3xwKFgJRHHW4pIB7RjQoJNfoJSBFyWzDDzY4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSchg3S-rvjk7DOky6yBCoby8EQMytbBE1eyYGyQe5rkIpSFcg%2Fviewform%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0miS_G0dUlNRbwJeACAkr3xwKFgJRHHW4pIB7RjQoJNfoJSBFyWzDDzY4&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=d8bde4a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSchg3S-rvjk7DOky6yBCoby8EQMy